OL,3,CSpray foam 'scam' threatens elderly
OL,4,Ccouple's downsizing dream
OL,6,FThey hoped to downsize, but have now
OL,7,Fbeen told the work damaged the roof
OL,8,Fand the property would be difficult to
OL,9,Fsell.
OL,11,FMrs Galley, 87, said: "It seemed the
OL,12,Fright thing to do for the environment
OL,13,F- we have an old house and it's cold."
OL,15,FShe added: "I've got arthritis and
OL,16,Fdifficulty getting up stairs, we are
OL,17,Fboth quite old so we thought we might
OL,18,Fsell it and get a bungalow.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
