OL,3,CSpray foam 'scam' threatens elderly
OL,4,Ccouple's downsizing dream
OL,6,F"We have been told that a buyer might
OL,7,Fhave difficulty getting a mortgage on
OL,8,Fit so it has really left us in limbo."
OL,10,FMrs Galley's son, Jon Galley said: "My
OL,11,Fmum and dad saw an advert and knew
OL,12,Fthat it was a government scheme so
OL,13,Fthey have trusted that.
OL,15,F"It's turned out to be little more
OL,16,Fthan a scam."
