OL,3,CSpray foam 'scam' threatens elderly
OL,4,Ccouple's downsizing dream
OL,6,FThe couple are among hundreds of
OL,7,Fthousands of homeowners who installed
OL,8,Fspray foam insulation, many of whom
OL,9,Ftook advantage of the now-defunct
OL,10,FGreen Homes scheme.
OL,12,FWhen installed properly, it can stop
OL,13,Fheat escaping from roofs, lofts and
OL,14,Fattics.
OL,16,FBut problems with poor fitting have
OL,17,Faffected many properties, leaving
OL,18,Fmoisture trapped and causing a risk of
OL,19,Fdecay to roof timbers.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
