OL,3,CSpray foam 'scam' threatens elderly
OL,4,Ccouple's downsizing dream
OL,6,FSeveral mortgage providers will now
OL,7,Fnot lend on properties with spray
OL,8,Finsulation.
OL,10,FThe family have been told that
OL,11,Fremoving the insulation will cost
OL,12,Faround #6,000 and could cause more
OL,13,Fdamage. A new roof could cost around
OL,14,F#20,000.
OL,16,FThe Chartered Trading Standards
OL,17,FInstitute said unreliable contractors
OL,18,Ftook advantage of government schemes.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
