OL,3,CSpray foam 'scam' threatens elderly
OL,4,Ccouple's downsizing dream
OL,6,FSteve Playle, a spokesperson from the
OL,7,FChartered Trading Standards Institute,
OL,8,Fsaid: "When the Green Homes grant was
OL,9,Ffirst announced by Rishi Sunak a few
OL,10,Fyears ago, within about two or three
OL,11,Fdays we noticed there were 40 or 50
OL,12,Fcompanies formed with companies house
OL,13,Fwith 'green homes' in the title.
OL,15,F"So that means there are lots of
OL,16,Fbusinesses out there that look to try
OL,17,Fand exploit grant funding schemes for
OL,18,Ftheir own means and rip customers off."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
