OL,4,Ccouple's downsizing dream
OL,6,FHe called for a national scheme to
OL,7,Fensure the work could only be carried
OL,8,Fout by licensed traders.
OL,10,FMrs Galley's MP, Tom Gordon, agrees
OL,11,Fthe Government should bear
OL,12,Fresponsibility for failing to oversee
OL,13,Frogue companies.
OL,15,FMr Gordon said: "If we want people to
OL,16,Ffuture-proof homes and encourage them
OL,17,Fto do that, not putting right previous
OL,18,Fschemes undermines that.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
