OL,6,F"It was a government backed scheme and
OL,7,Fgovernment funds that people drew
OL,8,Fdown, so to me it would be right for
OL,9,Fpeople to get some support and funds
OL,10,Ffrom the government."
OL,12,FA government spokesperson said the
OL,13,Fgovernment was "aware of the issue and
OL,14,Fhas consulted lenders who say they
OL,15,Frely on the views of valuers and
OL,16,Fsurveyors on this issue".
OL,18,FThey added: "Measures fitted under
OL,19,Fgovernment schemes must be fitted by a
OL,20,FTrustMark registered installer."
